ELEMENT.TITLE: FAQ - 2 Topics / 10/15 question per topic
ELEMENT.SUMMARY: This layout contains 25 Question and Answer text fields, broken out into a group of 10 and a group of 15 with topic headers for each of the two groups of faq. This set of FAQ is NOT tied into the profile.
ELEMENT.SHORT: Contains textboxes for 2 top level topics, and room for 25 questions and answers, 10 under one topic and 15 under the other.
